# Project Structure - AnnotateFlow Assistant

## Core Extension Files
- manifest.json           # Extension configuration
- background.js          # Service worker (main logic)
- content.js             # Content script for qlabel.tencent.com
- popup.html             # Extension popup interface
- popup.js               # Popup functionality

## Native Host Integration  
- native_host.py          # Native messaging host
- com.annotateflow.assistant.json  # Native host manifest
- install_native_host.bat # Installation script

## Documentation
- CLAUDE.md              # Project instructions for Claude Code
- README.md              # Main project documentation
- NATIVE_HOST_SETUP.md   # Native host setup guide
- SOUND_SETUP.md         # Audio setup instructions

## Configuration
- package.json           # Project metadata
- .git/                  # Git repository
- .claude/               # Claude Code settings

## Build Output
- dist/                  # Distribution files (if any)

Total Files: 15 core files (down from 30+ files)